Setting Type Default Description <code>LOAD_DEFAULT_CSS</code> <code>bool</code> <code>True</code> Loads the shared design-system stylesheet from <code>dj-control-room-base</code>. Set to <code>False</code> if a parent template already loads it. <code>EXTRA_CSS</code> <code>list[str]</code> <code>[]</code> Additional stylesheets to inject. Relative paths are resolved through Django's staticfiles system; absolute URLs are used as-is. <pre><code>DJ_DOOM_PANEL_SETTINGS = {
"LOAD_DEFAULT_CSS": True,
"EXTRA_CSS": [
"myapp/css/overrides.css",
"https://cdn.example.com/theme.css",
],
}
</code></pre>
